    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-cared for by its previous owner. The exterior paint still holds a nice shine, though you will notice some minor stone chips on the hood and a few light scratches consistent with regular use. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, with only slight wear on the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, it runs smoothly and has a consistent service history, making it a dependable choice for anyone looking for a quality pre-owned car without the showroom price tag.",
