    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained by its previous owner. The exterior retains a strong finish with only minor road wear and a few faint stone chips consistent with careful use. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, showing minimal wear on the upholstery and all electronics functioning as intended. It's a solid, reliable choice for anyone looking for a high-quality vehicle that is ready for the road.",
